ReadMe for pillarpanic Beta 1
--------------------------

Title:        Pillar Panic
Filename:     pillarpanicB1.pk3
Auther:       Poul Sander
Release Data: 2008-09-17
Version:      0.1 (Beta 1)
License:      GPL v2+

Play Information
----------------

                Game: Open arena 0.8.0
          Level Name: Pillar Panic
           Game Type: Elimination, DM, TDM
             Players: Elimination: 8-12, DM: 3-12, TDM 4-12
            Botmatch: Yes
       Single Player: Yes (Bots)
            Teamplay: No (Apart from TDM and Elimination)
        New Textures: No
          New Sounds: No
           New Music: No


Description
-------------
Very simple map mainly meant for Instantgib. There are nowhere to hide and there isalways someone behind you.

While variation is limited the map should be fun for most people as the map gives limited help to the 1337 ones.

Enjoy!
